<br>
As I continue my search, I can't help but wonder why she is there. Usually I can account for the reason, but this time I am stumped. I must know, or it will forever bother me. I open my worn spell book, turning to a page that has seen more use then any other page. Slowly I memorize the spell Ring of Commons, a destination all too familiar to me. As I memorize the spell I think back to my many adventures in the Commonslands.<br>
<br>
Slowly I cast the spell, wondering what I may find there, hoping I will soon know. <p><center>
