<br>
Kesryn stood like a noble high elf, staring Darkmask right back as Darkmask circled him, his robes sweeping in a circle behind him. The patrons watched unsure of what was going to happen, as Darkmask's head swept behind Kesryn he seemed to have a scowl on his face, but as he came around, a broad smile danced across his face and Darkmask patted Kesryn on the shoulder, " Welcome Dragon Lord, have you met my fiancee' Xanta " Darkmask knew full well she greeted him, but wanted to point out the word fiancee' to the Dragon Lord as was common among high elves to establish relationship grounds and to make it clear that her hand was taken.<br>
<br>
Darkmask ran to his bags, and dug through them, in a hurried manner, removing a hard bound book, he flipped a few pages and found the sketch. He showed Kesryn like an eager young child hoping Kesryn would recognize it.....he watched as the Dragon Lord traced his finger around the lines of the image, and pushed the sketch away.<br>
<br>
Confused, Darkmask decided not to press it anymore, sweeping behind Xanta, dropping the sketch book on the counter and wrapped his arms around her waist, and kissed her cheek.<br>
<br>
This was actually not done by high elves, public displays of affection are not common among the high elves, but Darkmask couldnt help himself, she just made him glow and electricty flowed from her into him. Xanta kissed his cheek back and rubbed the back of his head and slowly slipped from his grasp so she could serve some drinks.<br>
<br>
She looked back at him and eyed him, and smiled, he knew the look, all too well, he had seen it many times since droga and remembers it one time he saw it in Karnor's castle, she was pouring Dorraxx a little more to drink. " Darkmask, dear, I am quite famished would there be any chance you could make me something in the kitchen? " <br>
<br>
Darkmask eager to please, grabbed an apron and dissapeared into the kitchen to Dorraxx giggling, " That is the day, a woman who actually whipped Darkmask " to which Xanta giggled and bumped him with the side of her thigh and said " Shhhhhh, hes all mine and its wonderful, dont be jealous "<br>
<br>
To which Dorraxx turned towards the wall and muttered himself somethings about how he wasnt jealous, and how dwarves are very popular and how he has no reason to be jealous and drink down his ale all the way.<br>
<br>
Standing up very quickly, Dorraxx said, " I am going to get some firewood from out back, no one touch my drink " as he looked around, he considered for a moment, and swept his drink his hand and walked out the door......<br>
